# Modding Setup

- (Optional) Click 'Use this template' to make a new repository with this one as a base.
- Clone this or the new repository using `git clone <URL>`
- Run setup.ps1 and input the relevant information in the prompts it asks for.
- Open the generated sln file with your IDE of choice.

The project is set up to automatically copy the build files and required dlls to Thronefall/BepInEx/Plugins/<NameOfMod>
See https://docs.bepinex.dev/articles/dev_guide/plugin_tutorial/index.html on how to use BepInEx to modify the game.

## Useful libraries for development:

https://github.com/sinai-dev/UniverseLib - Library to work with the Unity UI through code and interop with other mods.
